<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Historiographical_debates_and_responsibility_of_France:_the_.22Vichy_Syndrome.22"><span class="tocnumber">11</span> <span class="toctext">Historiographical debates and responsibility of France: the "Vichy Syndrome"</span></a>
