istance_movement" title="Norwegian resistance movement">Norway</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hukbalahap" title="Hukbalahap">Philippines</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Polish_resistance_movement_in_World_War_II" title="Polish resistance movement in World War II">Poland</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Free_Thai_Movement" title="Free Thai Movement">Thailand</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Soviet_partisans" title="Soviet partisans">Soviet Union</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Slovak_National_Uprising" title="Slovak National Uprising">Slovakia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ukrainian_Insurgent_Army" title="Ukrainian Insurgent Army">Western Ukraine</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Viet_Minh" title="Viet Minh">Vietnam</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Yugoslavia" title="Kingdom of Yugoslavia">Yugoslavia</a> (<a href="/wiki/Yugoslav_Partisans" title="Yugoslav Partisans">Partisans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Chetniks" title="Chetniks">Chetniks</a>)</div>
